        {
            "title": "腦動極光折讓12%配股   集資5億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">腦動極光(06681)公布，以先舊後新方式配售股份，每股作價5.6元，較上日收市每股6.37元折讓約12.09%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"腦動極光年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/765x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260123_FI_06681_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"腦動極光年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/765x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260123_FI_06681_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">腦動極光年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">配售股份數量9200萬股，佔擴大後股本約6.77%，集資淨額約達5億元，當中50%用於研發，包括非侵入式腦機介面(BCI)干預系統及多模態大模型；30%用於國內及國際市場拓展；10%用於戰略投資及收購；餘下作一般營運資金。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">配售完成後，賣方及其一致行動人士持股將由40.95%攤薄至約38.18%，公司將按收購守則申請豁免全面要約責任。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15605013-%e8%85%a6%e5%8b%95%e6%a5%b5%e5%85%89%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9312%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1-%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%875%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/06681.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 08:39:25",
