            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期升278點  ADR高水148點  阿里巴巴高水近半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期升278點或1.05%，報26868。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR較恆指昨天收市高148點或0.56%，報26778點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_09988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣172.71元，較香港收市價高4.8%，影響恒指105點;京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣117.03元，較香港收市價詗.7%; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣595.08元，較香港收市價低0.4% ; 小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣35.62元，較香港收市價高1.1%，</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報130.62元，較香港收市價高0.7%;友邦保險(01299)，ADR收市折合港幣83.17元，較香港收市價0.8% ; 港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣427.5元，較香港收市價0.3%;中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣67.1元，較香港收市價0.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報26917點，升271點，較昨日恒指收市26629點，高水287點，成交20173張。國指夜市期指收報9212點，較昨日國指收市高水98點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15604992-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%8d%87278%e9%bb%9e-adr%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4148%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e8%bf%91%e5%8d%8a%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 08:26:02",
            "source": "bastillepost",
