            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英特爾首季展望遜預期　拖累盤後股價挫近13%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英特爾上季業績好過預期，但展望遜預期，拖累美股收市後股價急挫近13%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/Intel_at_CES_2024_24009101893393.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/Intel_at_CES_2024_24009101893393.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英特爾去年第4季虧損增至6億美元，按年擴大5倍。每股經調整盈利15美仙，高於預期的8美仙。上季收入137億美元，按年跌4%，但仍略高於預期。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">全年虧損3億美元，按年大幅收窄98%，每股經調整盈利42美仙。全年收入529億美元，基本持平。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集團預料，今季每股經調整後將不會錄得盈利，而市場預測為5美仙。收入估計介乎117億美元至127億美元，中位數122億美元，低於市場預期的125.1億美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英特爾預計，首季供應將跌至最低水平，第2季及之後將會改善，強調集團正積極擴大產能以滿足客戶需求。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15604990-%e8%8b%b1%e7%89%b9%e7%88%be%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%b1%95%e6%9c%9b%e9%81%9c%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f%e3%80%80%e6%8b%96%e7%b4%af%e7%9b%a4%e5%be%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e6%8c%ab%e8%bf%9113-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240802_FI_source-ap_Intel1_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 08:26:04",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價跌約2%　美國汽油庫存增至近5年高位",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價轉跌，由於地緣政治緊張局勢紓緩，美國總統特朗普緩和對格陵蘭及伊朗的威脅，市場也憧憬俄烏戰事解決。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油3月合約重回60美元以下，收報59.36美元，跌1.26美元，跌幅約2.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">倫敦布蘭特期油3月合約收報每桶64.06美元，跌1.18美元，跌幅1.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，美國能源信息署(EIA)數據顯示，美國上星期原油及成品油庫存都增加，由於煉廠及消費者需求都減少。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國上星期原油庫存增加360萬桶，增至4.26億桶，增幅高於預期。上星期汽油庫存增加600萬桶，增至2.57億桶，創近5年新高。蒸餾油庫存亦出乎意料增加335萬桶，增至1.33億桶，是兩年高位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15604920-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e8%b7%8c%e7%b4%842%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e6%b1%bd%e6%b2%b9%e5%ba%ab%e5%ad%98%e5%a2%9e%e8%87%b3%e8%bf%915%e5%b9%b4%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil_source-ap_-4.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 08:14:11",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股升1%或以上　德股未能收復25000點關口",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲股市造好，德國、法國、意大利及西班牙股市升1%或以上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市升1.03%，報608點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數連跌4日後回穩，但未能收復25000點關口，收報24856點，升295點，升幅1.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">法國CAC指數收報8148點，升79點，升幅1%，連升兩日，創近1星期新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國富時100指數同樣兩連升，早段升近0.9%，尾市升幅顯著收窄，收報10150點，升11點，升幅逾0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利富時MIB指數收報45091點，升1.36%或602點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報17663點，升1.28%或223點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">受潛在關稅威脅較大的歐洲汽車及藥品股急升，汽車股升2.3%，醫療保健股上漲1.7%，國防股受壓，德國萊茵金屬(Rheinmetall)急挫3.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15604912-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%871%e6%88%96%e4%bb%a5%e4%b8%8a%e3%80%80%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e6%9c%aa%e8%83%bd%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a925000%e9%bb%9e%e9%97%9c%e5%8f%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 08:09:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股兩連升　道指高收306點　Meta急升近6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股連續兩日造好，創約1星期收市新高，Meta收市炒高5.7%，亞馬遜及微軟均升超過1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國總統特朗普就收購格陵蘭問題收回對歐洲多國加徵關稅威脅，地緣政治緊張局勢緩和；美國去年第3季經濟按季增長年率向上修訂至4.4%，創兩年新高，10月及11月消費者開支穩健增長，均利好投資情緒。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">道瓊斯工業平均指數最多升530點，高見49607點，收報49384點，升306點，升幅逾0.6%。道指高開124點後，升幅擴大至最多530點，高見49607點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">標普500指數收報6913點，升37點，升幅0.55%，曾揚0.86%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">納斯達克指數收報23436點，升211點，升幅0.9%，一度漲1.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科技股大多造好，Meta急升5.7%，Tesla升4.2%。Netflix仍未止跌，低收逾2%，連跌6日，再創逾1年新低。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3M升3.1%，為表現最佳道指成份股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">多隻記憶體相關股份持續創新高，但升幅普遍少於上日，其中，美光升2.18%，連升5日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">業績股個別發展，雅培及通用航空航天績後分別大跌10%及7.38%，寶潔升2.66%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英特爾收市後公布的業績展望不及預期，市後股價急挫逾6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15604922-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a9%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87%e3%80%80%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6306%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80meta%e6%80%a5%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%916-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 08:09:16",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金價突破4900美元創新高　銀價破頂升穿96美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價升勢持續，突破每盎司4900美元關口，再創新高。市場注視地緣政局發展，加上美元走弱、分析預料聯儲局今年仍會減息，都支持金價走勢。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"銀價 (Shutterstock圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source_licensed_shutterstock_2009158820.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"銀價 (Shutterstock圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source_licensed_shutterstock_2009158820.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">銀價 (Shutterstock圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">現貨金較早時徘徊每盎司4938美元以上，升約2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期金2月合約收報4913.4美元，升約1.6%，較早時升至4944美元附近。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">現貨白銀一度升至每盎司約96.58美元，創新高。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15604910-%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e7%aa%81%e7%a0%b44900%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e9%8a%80%e5%83%b9%e7%a0%b4%e9%a0%82%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf96%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240917_PL_gold_source-licensed_1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-23 08:09:18",
